title: 10/18/21 DPS Hour 3 Carson Palmer

description:
Carson Palmer talks to Dan about Jared Goff and his head coach's remarks at his press conference. Carson says he was called out before because when you win, the QB gets too much props, and when you lose, the QB gets too much blame.
